  <h3>Markdown Syntax (<a target="_blank" title="Markdown Basic" href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/basics">official guide</a>)</h3>
  <div class="content">

<h4>Phrase Emphasis</h4> 
 
<pre><code>*italic*   **bold**
_italic_   __bold__
</code></pre>

<h4>Headers</h4>

<pre><code>Header 1
========

Header 2
--------

### Header 3

#### Header 4
</code></pre>


<h4>Links</h4>

<pre><code>[stroome it!](http://stroome.com)

[info@stroome.com](mailto:info@stroome.com)
</code></pre>

<h4>Manual Line Breaks</h4>

<p>End a line with two or more spaces:</p>

<pre><code>Roses are red,   
Violets are blue.
</code></pre> 

    
<h4>Lists</h4> 
 
<p>Ordered, without paragraphs:</p> 
 
<pre><code>1.  Foo
2.  Bar
</code></pre> 
 
<p>Unordered, with paragraphs:</p> 
 
<pre><code>*   A list item.
 
    With multiple paragraphs.
 
*   Bar
</code></pre> 
 
<p>You can nest them:</p> 
 
<pre><code>*   Abacus
    * answer
*   Bubbles
    1.  bunk
    2.  bupkis
        * BELITTLER
    3. burper
*   Cunning
</code></pre> 

